ll there''s a whole lot of difference with the way you''re communicating with me. You''re more confident. There''s not much filler words. Yeah. For, yeah, for you know?\n\nYeah. It it''s practice makes perfect. So I can I can I can give you something to to work on, like, on yourself? This is not about recording. You can probably if you have a standing mirror, you can or you can place your phone and just record yourself with some answers or some with some questions and try to record yourself without the filler words.\n\nTry to do it, like, 5 times and play it again and watch yourself. You will understand you you will see the difference of when there''s filler words and no filler words. You you you''ll be able to appreciate it more, and it gives you more confidence. Okay? So now at the end at the end of this session and 1 more thing 1 more thing.\n\nI would appreciate if you have the time. You can probably leave, like, a review on my profile just if yeah. So, see, I''ll I''ll really appreciate that. So now at the end of this session, I want you to send a voice note. A voice note.\n\nLike, 212, or 3. Don''t rush. Just take your time. You can just take a cup of coffee, and you send a very calm voice note, like a confident speaker, like the boss, you know, like the relaxed numbers I know, and just talk about your session today. Today, I''m so happy to learn about the filler words, and I can now speak more without adding much of the filler words.\n\nSo you just give me that voice note. Any amount. Any. Any. You can you can give me 5.\n\nYou can give me 4. Send them. Send as much as I want to hear them. Send as much as possible. Okay?\n\nYou can send 1. Don''t worry about it. If if you send 1, don''t delete. Send again. Send again.\n\nWhen you feel when you feel you''re you got it right, then you leave it for me. Yes. Then wait for my reply. And just just there''s no limit. You can send as much as possible.\n\nI want to listen. I want to be happy. I want to be happy. It''s being effective in your communication. Okay?\n\nSo that when you speak amongst anyone, I want them to feel that presence, that confidence. Because when you when you take your time, that is no rush. That is power. That is confidence. And that''s what I wanna see more in you.\n\nYes. Alright. Bye. Yeah.", "paragraphs": [{"sentences": [{"text": "I can tell there''s a whole lot of difference with the way you''re communicating with me.", "start": 0, "end": 4.8}, {"text": "You''re more confident.", "start": 4.88, "end": 6.08}, {"text": "There''s not much filler words.", "start": 6.08, "end": 8.959999}, {"text": "Yeah.", "start": 9.36, "end": 10.08}, {"text": "For, yeah, for you know?", "start": 10.32, "end": 12.4}], "num_words": 30, "start": 0, "end": 12.4}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Yeah.", "start": 17.185, "end": 17.585}, {"text": "It it''s practice makes perfect.", "start": 17.585, "end": 21.345}, {"text": "So I can I can I can give you something to to work on, like, on yourself?", "start": 21.744999, "end": 28.759998}, {"text": "This is not about recording.", "start": 28.759998, "end": 30.199999}, {"text": "You can probably if you have a standing mirror, you can or you can place your phone and just record yourself with some answers or some with some questions and try to record yourself without the filler words.", "start": 30.439999, "end": 43.559998}], "num_words": 66, "start": 17.185, "end": 43.559998}, {"sentences": [{"text": "Try to do it, like, 5 times and play it again and watch yourself.", "start": 44.265, "end": 48.745}, {"text": "You will understand you you will see the difference of when there''s filler words and no filler words.", "start": 49.065, "end": 54.825}, {"text": "You you you''ll be able to appreciate it more, and it gives you more confidence.", "start": 54.825, "end": 59.079998}, {"text": "Okay?", "start": 59.079998, "end": 59.719997}, {"text": "So now at the end at the end of this session and 1 more thing 1 more thing.", "start": 59.72, "end": 64.